M. S. El Sawah, Appellant, v State Insurance Fund, Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, without costs, for reasons stated at Special Term, Patlow, J. (Appeal from order of Supreme Court, Monroe County, Patlow, J. — summary judgment.) Present — Hancock, Jr., J. P., Callahan, Green, O’Donnell and Moule, JJ.
